---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Demo Model Program – Bliss Dermacare" description="Apply to be a demo model at Bliss Dermacare. Get professional skincare treatments at 50–80% off in Tampa, FL. Same quality, reduced pricing.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-[#faf9f7] border-b border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4 block">Save Big on Real Treatments</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">Demo Model Program</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600">Professional-grade skincare at 50–80% off. Same products. Same expertise. Reduced pricing in exchange for feedback.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Info + Form Section -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">

        <!-- Left: Info -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">How the Program Works</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">The Demo Model Program is designed to give clients access to the same professional treatments at a significantly reduced rate. In return, you provide honest feedback, allow us to document results (with your permission), and help us demonstrate our techniques.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Submit Your Application</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Fill out the form with your skin type, concerns, and what you're hoping to achieve.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1">We'll Review & Reach Out</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">We'll contact you within 24–48 hours to discuss which treatments make the most sense for you.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Get Your Discounted Session</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Same professional treatment, same products, same care — at 50–80% off standard pricing.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-200 space-y-3">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">What's included?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Same products and professional equipment used for all clients</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Personalized skin assessment included</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Before/after photos (optional — with your written consent only)</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>50–80% off standard service pricing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-5 text-sm">
            <p class="text-amber-900 font-medium mb-1">Availability is limited</p>
            <p class="text-amber-800">Demo model slots are offered based on scheduling and the specific techniques being practised. Not all services are available as demo sessions at all times.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Application Form -->
        <div>
          <div class="bg-[#faf9f7] rounded-2xl p-8 border border-neutral-200">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-6">Apply to Be a Demo Model</h2>

            <form
              name="demo-model-application"
              method="POST"
              data-netlify="true"
              action="/demo-model/?submitted=demo-model"
              class="space-y-5"
            >
              <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="demo-model-application" />

              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div>
                  <label for="demoName" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Full Name *</label>
                  <input type="text" id="demoName" name="name" required placeholder="Jane Smith"
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm bg-white" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label for="demoPhone" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Phone *</label>
                  <input type="tel" id="demoPhone" name="phone" required placeholder="(609) 366-0857"
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm bg-white" />
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="demoEmail" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Email *</label>
                <input type="email" id="demoEmail" name="email" required placeholder="jane@example.com"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm bg-white" />
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="demoSkinType" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Skin Type *</label>
                <select id="demoSkinType" name="skin-type" required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm bg-white">
                  <option value="">Select your skin type...</option>
                  <option value="normal">Normal</option>
                  <option value="dry">Dry</option>
                  <option value="oily">Oily</option>
                  <option value="combination">Combination</option>
                  <option value="sensitive">Sensitive</option>
                  <option value="not-sure">Not Sure</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="demoConcern" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Primary Skin Concern *</label>
                <select id="demoConcern" name="skin-concern" required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm bg-white">
                  <option value="">Select your main concern...</option>
                  <option value="acne">Acne / Breakouts</option>
                  <option value="aging">Signs of Aging / Wrinkles</option>
                  <option value="hyperpigmentation">Dark Spots / Hyperpigmentation</option>
                  <option value="texture">Uneven Skin Texture</option>
                  <option value="dryness">Dryness / Dehydration</option>
                  <option value="redness">Redness / Sensitivity</option>
                  <option value="general">General Maintenance</option>
                  <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="demoNotes" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Tell us about your skin & goals</label>
                <textarea id="demoNotes" name="notes" rows="4" placeholder="Any allergies, past treatments, skincare products you're currently using, or specific results you're hoping for..."
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm resize-none bg-white"></textarea>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <input type="checkbox" id="demoConsent" name="photo-consent" value="yes" class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 accent-primary-600 flex-shrink-0" />
                <label for="demoConsent" class="text-xs text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">I consent to before/after photos being taken for educational and promotional purposes. Photos will not be shared without my written permission.</label>
              </div>

              <button type="submit"
                class="w-full bg-primary-600 text-white py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all font-semibold text-base shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
                Submit Application
              </button>

              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 text-center">We'll review your application and reach out within 24–48 hours.</p>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
